overview:
MAP-IT Inc. Provides Best Quality Marketing and Advertising Solutions, Graphics Design, Website Design and Development, Internet Marketing, Printing & OutdoorMedia.

Full Service Branding and Marketing Company, MAP-IT, Inc. which was launched on July 1st 2011. The basis of this company is to provide marketing solutions to small -mid size businesses, entrepreneurs and start-ups. We help them “Map it” out, where they are today and where they would like to be 5 - 10 years from now. We bring their vision together and help them reach their target market by way of innovative marketing technologies & solutions hence the name - MAP = Marketing, Advertising & Promoting It.
